## Known Issues (Python)

- **Python base image (glibc):** Trivy may report CVE-2026-0861 (libc6) until Debian backports a fix. In Dockerfile production stage, run `apt-get update && apt-get upgrade -y` before installing packages so the next base update is picked up; track [Debian CVE-2026-0861](https://security-tracker.debian.org/tracker/CVE-2026-0861).
- **pytest-asyncio 1.x:** Add `asyncio_mode = "auto"` to pyproject.toml
- **isort 7.x:** Use `profile = "black"` in pyproject.toml

## Version Policy

1. **Patch:** Apply freely
2. **Minor:** Test in reference project first
3. **Major:** Coordinate across projects, update this doc
4. **Security:** Apply immediately
5. **Production:** Pin exact versions in requirements.txt/lockfiles
